title.rendered: Kylie Jenner: Her First Modeling Shoot

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

At least she isn’t wearing a bikini.

Just days after sister Kendall made her official, controversial modeling debut, 12-year old Kylie Jenner has become the latest girl in the Kardashian/Jenner clan to pose professionally.

Kylie has been chosen by Sears to appear in a series of fall TV commercials to promote the chain’s “Crush Your Style – The Search for America’s Top Style Crush” contest.

As you might expect, older sisters Kim and Khloe Kardashian have already Tweeted their support, as the former wrote: “So proud of u Kylie! my sisters are superstars!” and the latter chimed in with: “OMG I’m such a proud parent right now LOL!”

Looks like Kylie is well on her way to joining her attention-starved family on tabloid covers and reality shows. Please, please, someone keep Ray J away from her.
